Package net.maswag.falcaun.parser

Class ExtendedSignalMapperBaseListener

java.lang.Object
net.maswag.falcaun.parser.ExtendedSignalMapperBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
ExtendedSignalMapperListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class ExtendedSignalMapperBaseListener extends Object implements ExtendedSignalMapperListener
This class provides an empty implementation of ExtendedSignalMapperListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
